{"tid":454032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侮辱中國國歌可重囚三年政治監","createTime":"2017-10-31T18:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T10:37:27.000Z","uid":47359,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"809568b8e3d37726d268a494d7af1dd3ba240e08","tid":454032,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1744838838957498&amp;id=715486135226112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1744838838957498%26id%3D715486135226112&d=XhJKvJGZCZrAMg57pUK6GDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1ccb5916\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1744838838957498&amp;id=715486135226112</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會建議在刑法修正案，將侮辱國歌的刑罰，與侮辱國旗、國徽看齊，情節嚴重者，可判處3年以下有期徒刑、役、管制或者剝奪政治權利。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨議員涂謹申說，個人不贊成市民在公開場合貶損或侮辱國歌，但認為在本地立法時，很多技術細節要小心處理。他說國旗和國徽是有形體，但國歌是聲音、是奏唱，他舉例說，若在大球場內奏唱國歌，門外正排隊買票的人應怎樣回應，認為就國歌法本地立法時要按香港的情況制定。涂謹申又認為，國歌法不應該設追溯期，以免出現用今日的法例處理昨日行為的情況。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #國歌法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9927b8996e9c6e906583de55bab49fabe3dec4","tid":454032,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T18:08:14.000Z","msg":"人見人愛<br />\n朋!友!愛!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b59c9540919b4b508a476c13db1ebf3bc6d5440","tid":454032,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T18:09:32.000Z","msg":"到時唱歌有懶音都捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5f84457bef098631e9e38592388b158fbfdf0e","tid":454032,"uid":141421,"like":3,"dislike":33,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T18:09:42.000Z","msg":"我個人認為合理"},{"pid":"242e5fe5b8409490cb23fcccb4ceb61e2b2924d9","tid":4